				"These hatches will start to unlock from EV."
				""
				"How are they different from normal hatches? These send 4 Amps to a machine, meaning it will act as if you use 2 normal energy hatches. But! Using only 1 hatch will NOT overclock the machine, meaning you can only use recipes on tier with the energy hatch. If you use 2 hatches, it will overclock normally."
				""
				"These come in 4, 8 and 16 Amp variants."
				""
				"The fastest combo of hatches is using 2 16 Amp hatches, but if you don't have the energy generation, this will eat through your power."
